{"author":{"id":"b78c39e7b13f90a5827abfba043255fe7a4ede1499df23f110fffe5abfa44adc"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1769629803,"nonce":"Nnvd2ozbAMWuMChyXnErRYw7fHc=","metadata":{"github-id":"I_kwDOQ241x87mf2sk","github-url":"https://github.com/rolker/ros2_agent_workspace/issues/109","origin":"github"},"title":"Add PR review workflow to streamline addressing review comments","message":"## Problem\nNo streamlined workflow for checking and addressing PR review comments. Agents must:\n1. Manually run `gh pr view \u003cnumber\u003e`\n2. Parse review comments\n3. Figure out which comments need action\n4. Address them one by one\n\nThis is inefficient for iterative PR review cycles.\n\n## Example Friction\nUser said: \"Can you check on the PR and address review comments?\"\n\nAgent had to:\n```bash\ngh pr view 34 --json reviews,comments\n# Parse JSON manually\n# Identify 2 review comments\n# Address each comment separately\n```\n\n## Proposed Solution\n\nAdd PR review commands to `.agent/CLI_COMMANDS.md`:\n\n### `/check-pr-reviews`\n**Script**: `.agent/scripts/check_pr_reviews.sh`\n\nShows all PRs with pending review comments:\n```\nPR #34 - Test infrastructure setup\n  Review by copilot[bot]:\n    ✗ test_placeholder.cpp:10 - Duplicate main() function\n    ✗ CMakeLists.txt:39 - Non-existent include directory\n  \n  Action: Run /pr-address 34\n```\n\n### `/pr-status \u003cnumber\u003e`\n**Script**: `.agent/scripts/pr_status.sh \u003cnumber\u003e`\n\nDetailed PR status with actionable items:\n- Review comments (grouped by file)\n- CI status\n- Merge conflicts\n- Requested changes vs approved\n- Suggested next steps\n\n## Implementation\n\nUse GitHub CLI:\n```bash\ngh pr view $PR_NUM --json reviews,reviewRequests,comments,statusCheckRollup\n```\n\nParse and present:\n- Comments requiring code changes\n- Unresolved threads\n- CI failures\n- Merge conflicts\n\n## Impact\n- ✅ Faster PR review cycles\n- ✅ Don't miss review comments\n- ✅ Clear action items\n- ✅ Reduces back-and-forth with user\n\n## Priority\n🟡 Medium - Improves efficiency during PR review cycles\n\n## Session Evidence\nSession: 66b4eea3-8aff-4a81-88b6-6aafd77a65e3\n- User: \"Can you check on the PR and address review comments?\"\n- Had to manually retrieve PR, parse 2 review comments\n- Would benefit from automated extraction and formatting\n- Fixed both comments successfully, but workflow could be smoother\n\n---\n**🤖 Reported-By**: Copilot CLI Agent (Claude Sonnet 4.5)","files":null}]}